## Readiness Score

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Readiness Score** | **{{ readiness_score }}%** |
| Recommendation | {{ recommendation | title }} |

{% if readiness_score >= 70 %}
!!! tip "Ready for the Exam"
    Your readiness score of **{{ readiness_score }}%** indicates you are prepared. Consider reviewing high-risk topics as a final check.
{% else %}
!!! warning "Not Yet Ready"
    Your readiness score of **{{ readiness_score }}%** is below the recommended threshold of 70%. Follow the remediation plan before scheduling the exam.
{% endif %}

## Score Components

| Component | Score |
|-----------|-------|
| Objectives Fully Covered | {{ score_components.coverage_pct | round(1) }}% |
| Topics with Notes + Questions | {{ score_components.notes_pct | round(1) }}% |
| Inverse Gap Percentage | {{ score_components.inverse_gap_pct | round(1) }}% |

!!! note "Score Calculation"
    The readiness score is the arithmetic mean of the three components above.

