## Recommendation

{% if recommendation == "ready" %}
!!! tip "Proceed with Confidence"
    Based on your preparation level, you are ready to take the GH-600 exam. Review the high-risk topics below for a final confidence boost.
{% else %}
!!! important "Defer Exam"
    Based on your current preparation level, it is recommended to defer the exam and follow the remediation plan. Focus on the high-risk topics and last-minute areas identified below.
{% endif %}

